  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of gpgme</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>gpgme</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

../configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the results, you should have <xref linkend="gnupg2"/>
      installed. If so, run:
    </para>

<screen remap='test'><userinput>make -k check</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the &root; user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

